episodes.title: how this vegan trans cult turned into PSYCHOTIC killers | Zizians
episodes.description:
The Zizians were a group of gifted thinkers who believed they could solve morality through logic, but their ideas slowly twisted into something dark and violent. What started as a search for truth became a descent into obsession, control, and murder.
